snippet.textDisplay:
I have always loved Ustad Nusrat Fateh Ali Khan Saab's versions, both the slow starting to fast, and the explosive one in Islamabad. This one the recording was insane, the Tabla took me to a different dimension and the voices blended so beautifully. How upset I was to hear that one of the singers, whom I just heard about, left this Earth so young.

My dear brothers from Pakistan, would one of you be so kind as to translate the song lyrics for me so I can connect with it at a deeper level?
snippet.textOriginal:
